Occurrence remarks: 2 stags, there have been frequent sightings in the last few weeks of up to10 individuals after gap of 12 months or so. They have only been seen in the area in the last 3- 4 years. As the sighting is from the other side of the valley,I havent been able to get photo evidence yet, as would need telephoto lens but will try to do so.  It's fantastic red deer habitat with access to many miles of moorland and clough and valley side woodland.  They have been raiding the sheep haylage today.
